title: Estrada or Nada
description: A new game show where contestants challenge the greatest star in the history of television to any competiton imaginable. Hot dog eating, fencing, sewing, violining, and even lumberjacking! Judged by a panel including a Hollywood stunt man, a former olympian, and a morning show DJ.
